            <a href="..\/images\/4396_4001158.jpg" class="enlargement-link enlargement-link-47149"><img src="images/4396_4001160.jpg" alt="Mao" title="Andy Warhol
American, 1928-1987, Mao"  /></a>          </div>

    <p class="tools">
              <a href="..\/images\/4396_4001158.jpg" class="enlargement-link enlargement-link-47149"><strong>View</strong> enlargement</a><br />
                          <a href="http://www.artic.edu/aic/collections/exhibitions/Modern/artwork/47149/email"><strong>Email</strong> to a friend</a><br />
